                                <h1>
                                    World Certification
                                    <br>Industry Association
                                </h1>
                                <div class="text">
									The WIA International Qualification Test is the CERTIFIED DIGITAL ASSET MANAGER(CDM), CERTIFIED BLOCKCHAIN MANAGER(CBM) conducted by the World Certification Industry Association(WIA), CERTIFIED METAVERSE MANAGER(CMM), CERTIFIED NFT MANAGER(CNM), CERTIFIED IFPS MANAGER(CDM), CERTIFIED SAFETY EDUCATION MANAGER(CEM), CERTIFIED ESG MANAGER(ESG), etc.
									<!--
										WIA's main business is a certification project that can nurture masters in each industry in the era of the 4th industrial revolution and Web 3.0.
										It fosters International Certified Blockchain Manager(CBM), International Certified Metaverse Manager(CMM), International Certified NFT Manager(CNM), International Cetified Digital Assets Manager(CDM), International Certified IFPS Manager (CDM), and International Certified safety Education Manager(CEM) ···etc.
									-->
                                </div>
                                <div class="market-status">
