									<p>
                                    Join the development of the World Certification Industry Association(WIA).<br>
									We are currently accepting cryptocurrency donations. Bitcoin, Ethereum and USDT.
									</p>
									<br>
									<p>WIA - 0x40ddf5e260e4766cca9553843b4e8caacae9c1ca</p>
