                    <div class="title">ABOUT WIA</div>
                </div>
                <div class="row clearfix">
                    <!-- Content Column -->
                    <div class="content-column col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                        <div class="inner-column">
                            <div class="text">
                                The WIA Tech Incubator Program for Startup fosters promising startups by selecting a funding team with tech items that will lead the global market. To provide bold founding opportunities for promising startups with global market-oriented technology, we designate successful venture-oriented investment companies, early VCs, and large techology companies and match investment, technology education, and mentoring with R＆D funds.
                            </div>
                            <div class="blocks-outer">
                                <!-- Feature Block -->
                                <div class="feature-block">
                                    <div class="inner-box">
                                        <div class="icon flaticon-technical-support"></div>
                                        <h6>Startup Team</h6>
                                        <div class="feature-text">
                                            Start a business with a technology item without the burden of failure
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
